OL,3,CFamily and UN urge release of Gaza
OL,4,Cdoctor detained by Israel
OL,6,FThe son of Dr Hussam Abu Safiya says
OL,7,Fhe is "in solitary confinement and
OL,8,Fregularly subjected to beatings and
OL,9,Ftorture", as ITV News Correspondent
OL,10,FGeraint Vincent reports
OL,12,FIt is one of the most famous images
OL,13,Ffrom the war in Gaza.
OL,15,FA doctor in a white coat walking
OL,16,Facross the rubble in a ruined street,
OL,17,Fmaking his way from his hospital
OL,18,Ftowards two Israeli armoured vehicles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
