OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783702081
OL,3,CFamily and UN urge release of Gaza
OL,4,Cdoctor detained by Israel
OL,6,FDoctor Hussam Abu Safiya was the
OL,7,Fdirector of the Kamal Adwan hospital
OL,8,Fin northern Gaza. In December 2024, he
OL,9,Fkept the hospital running for weeks as
OL,10,Fthe surrounding neighborhood was
OL,11,Fbombed and besieged.
OL,13,FIsraeli forces suspected the hospital
OL,14,Fwas being used as a Hamas stronghold,
OL,15,Fand had summoned Dr Hussam to talk to
OL,16,Fhim about its evacuation.
OL,18,FThe paediatrician ended up being
OL,19,Fdetained on suspicion of terrorist
OL,20,Factivity. He has been in prison in
OL,21,FIsrael ever since.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783702081
OL,3,CFamily and UN urge release of Gaza
OL,4,Cdoctor detained by Israel
OL,6,FHis son Elyias told ITV News that his
OL,7,Ffather had been subjected to torture
OL,8,Fand beatings and was being kept in
OL,9,Fsolitary confinement in conditions
OL,10,Fthat are cruel and inhuman.
OL,12,FIsrael's Prison Service described the
OL,13,Fallegations of torture and abuse as
OL,14,Ffalse and entirely without factual
OL,15,Fbasis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
