CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783702081
OL,3,CFamily and UN urge release of Gaza
OL,4,Cdoctor detained by Israel
OL,6,FThe last time Dr Hussam was seen was
OL,7,Fon a video link to a courtroom. He sat
OL,8,Fsilent and gaunt as his latest appeal
OL,9,Ffor release was denied on the basis of
OL,10,Fevidence, which the Israeli
OL,11,Fauthorities describe as confidential.
OL,13,FThe United Nations has called for his
OL,14,Fimmediate release, with its human
OL,15,Frights council commenting: "The
OL,16,Fpractice of medicine is not a crime."
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
