PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783702081
OL,3,CFamily and UN urge release of Gaza
OL,4,Cdoctor detained by Israel
OL,6,FThe campaign group Physicians for
OL,7,FHuman Rights is petitioning Israeli
OL,8,Fauthorities for the release of
OL,9,Ffourteen Palestinian doctors from Gaza
OL,10,F- all of whom, it says, are being held
OL,11,Fwithout charge.
OL,13,FDr Hussam was originally detained on
OL,14,Fsuspicion of terrorist activity.
OL,15,FElyias says his father's only crime
OL,16,Fwas to be a compassionate doctor,
OL,17,Fagainst whom the Israeli military held
OL,18,Fa grudge because he refused to leave
OL,19,Fhis post.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
